{"tid":630650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港地就好似成龍咁","createTime":"2018-04-15T18:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T20:00:14.000Z","uid":45148,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"782d79c519c6bf7730035b65cd972b03cbeec1b1","tid":630650,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:22:02.000Z","msg":"香港地就好似成龍咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成龍係Chinese功夫既代名詞<br />\n<br />\n代表左一代香港影星既icon<br />\n<br />\n有實力，懂功夫<br />\n<br />\n有演技<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但作為香港既你，聽到成龍 兩個字真係得淡笑<br />\n<br />\n聽到房祖名 又係得淡笑<br />\n<br />\n聽到吳綺莉 又係得淡笑<br />\n<br />\n聽到吳卓林 都係得淡笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯，香港影視業上到世界舞台，成龍可能係最出名果個，<br />\n唔少外國人諗起香港電影，就會諗起成龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成龍彷佛成爲香港代名詞<br />\n<br />\n但睇緊呢個post 既你 只可以得淡笑<br />\n因為呢個係事實<br />\n但唔係事實既全部"},{"pid":"346f10c3e971de09984bd615a001497fe618cbd2","tid":630650,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:33:30.000Z","msg":"成龍有功夫？有演技？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係呀！"},{"pid":"9cfb1e7b3abe1097162946e8e538384ea1cf6621","tid":630650,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346f10c3e971de09984bd615a001497fe618cbd2","tid":630650,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:33:30.000Z","msg":"成龍有功夫？有演技？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係呀！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:56:22.000Z","msg":"無演技但有好多人睇？<br />\n<br />\n咁講星爺都無演技<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星爺一個金像獎都未攞過"},{"pid":"86fd59d744156904dd66f453be746d1ca24feea1","tid":630650,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T18:57:35.000Z","msg":"房事龍條撚樣同埋佢個仔一齊食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46fbeb1e4e2254e506f28dbcc911fae484c87d3","tid":630650,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9cfb1e7b3abe1097162946e8e538384ea1cf6621","tid":630650,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346f10c3e971de09984bd615a001497fe618cbd2","tid":630650,"uid"